### multi-UI local workflows
here I can provision PTS and TGM simultaneously, and make a change to `mdaUiLib` and see it immediately reflected in both

Change your UI CLI aliases such that

1.  each package has a different `--bundler-port` e.g. `--bundler-port 50082` on one and `--bundler-port 50081` on another
2.  each package has a different `-W` working dir.
    1.  I do this for logging and workdir
    2.  `~/dev/c3log/<package_name>` and `~/dev/uiWorkingDir/<package_name>`

`Example aliases`

alias ui-mda='c3 ui --log-dir ~/dev/c3log/mdaTrajectory --with-tests -W ~/c3/uiWorkingDir/mdaTrajectory -e [http://mdatrajectory:8080](http://mdatrajectory:8080 "http://mdatrajectory:8080/") -t mdaTrajectory:dev -a ~/c3/c3fed-mda/mda -u BA:BA --bundler-port 50081'
